INSTALL - GPU Batch Blur

Prerequisites:
  - CUDA Toolkit >= 11.0  (includes NPP)
  - OpenCV 4.x            (sudo apt install libopencv-dev)
  - g++ / nvcc
  - pkg-config

Ubuntu/Debian:
  sudo apt update
  sudo apt install libopencv-dev pkg-config

Build:
  make build

Run (auto-downloads dataset):
  ./run.sh

Manual run:
  ./bin/blur.exe -i data/images -o data/output
